\e[91m ========= \e[97mCzo System Rescue %ISO_VERSION% (%ISO_DATE%)\e[91m ======== \e[97m\l\e[91m =========

            \e[91mhttps://gitlab.com/czo/czo-system-rescue

\e[31m*\e[01;31m Console environment\e[m :
   Run \e[01;37msetkmap\e[00;37m to choose the keyboard layout

\e[31m*\e[01;31m Graphical environment\e[m :
   Type \e[01;37mstartx\e[00;37m to run the graphical environment

\e[31m*\e[01;31m Change cowspace\e[m :
   mount -o remount,size=1G /run/archiso/cowspace

